title: IAA Tonight | Will Lamar's Next Big Deal be in Baltimore?
description: Since the Ravens and Lamar Jackson can't agree on a deal before his deadline, what will be the next move for the star QB? Could this potentially be the beginning of the end for Lamar being the QB for the Baltimore Ravens. Plus, SiriusXM NFL Radio Host Kirk Morrison joins to discuss the Rams getting wrecked on opening night of the 2022 NFL season. What do the defending Super Bowl champs have to do in order for spectators to believe they can repeat and win it all again?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Ashley Nicole Moss, Omar KElly, Chantel Tremetiere)
